      "body" : "I don't think we should do it this way. CoinControlDialog::coinControl should not be used if getCoinControlFeatures is disabled. It may have invalid state.\r\nWhat about creating a temporary CoinControl object and just changing the confirmation setting in the case of non-coin-control? This will ensure it's at least starting from defaults.\r\n",
